00:46:09.236 --> 00:46:12.876
We have a trial open at Yale with Barbara as the PI, and Mike

774
00:46:12.916 --> 00:46:14.276
Tarazi, who's in the audience,

775
00:46:15.116 --> 00:46:18.796
has a poster tomorrow describing the effects of this therapy to

776
00:46:18.876 --> 00:46:22.736
