779
00:46:32.956 --> 00:46:36.795
And so here we have shown that activating NF-kappa B

780
00:46:36.915 --> 00:46:40.436
signaling can sensitize high-risk tumors to

781
00:46:40.456 --> 00:46:43.756
radiation and that entolimod allows us to

782
00:46:43.816 --> 00:46:45.896
