783
00:46:47.016 --> 00:46:50.676
The improved therapeutic ratio should improve tumor control by

784
00:46:50.736 --> 00:46:52.556
decreasing radiation side effects.

785
00:46:54.036 --> 00:46:57.236
Understanding the biology of these subtypes reframes

786
00:46:58.116 --> 00:47:02.016
how we think about tumor de-escalation, not as a global

787
00:47:02.136 --> 00:47:05.576
strategy, but as one that must be biologically selective.

788
00:47:06.376 --> 00:47:10.136
And we now have a biomarker to help

789
00:47:10.176 --> 00:47:10.956
guide therapy.

790
00:47:12.156 --> 00:47:15.956
What's exciting to me is that these findings have the potential to

791
00:47:16.016 --> 00:47:19.516
move us from imprecise patient selection to

792
00:47:19.556 --> 00:47:22.656
predictive decision-making for care of these patients.

